item.description: A*STAR (Agency for Science, Technology and Research) is a key research organization of the Singapore government, dedicated to promoting scientific and technological research and driving economic growth through innovation. A*STAR conducts both fundamental and applied research across multiple fields and works closely with industry and academia.
